            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Kings%203%3A3-4%3A34%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESolomon%20loved%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20followed%20all%20the%20decrees%20of%20his%20father%2C%20David%2C%20except%20that%20Solomon%2C%20too%2C%20offered%20sacrifices%20and%20burned%20incense%20at%20the%20local%20places%20of%20worship.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20most%20important%20of%20these%20places%20of%20worship%20was%20at%20Gibeon%2C%20so%20the%20king%20went%20there%20and%20sacrificed%201%2C000%20burnt%20offerings.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThat%20night%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20appeared%20to%20Solomon%20in%20a%20dream%2C%20and%20God%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20do%20you%20want%3F%20Ask%2C%20and%20I%20will%20give%20it%20to%20you!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESolomon%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20showed%20great%20and%20faithful%20love%20to%20your%20servant%20my%20father%2C%20David%2C%20because%20he%20was%20honest%20and%20true%20and%20faithful%20to%20you.%20And%20you%20have%20continued%20to%20show%20this%20great%20and%20faithful%20love%20to%20him%20today%20by%20giving%20him%20a%20son%20to%20sit%20on%20his%20throne.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNow%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20my%20God%2C%20you%20have%20made%20me%20king%20instead%20of%20my%20father%2C%20David%2C%20but%20I%20am%20like%20a%20little%20child%20who%20doesn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20know%20his%20way%20around.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20here%20I%20am%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20your%20own%20chosen%20people%2C%20a%20nation%20so%20great%20and%20numerous%20they%20cannot%20be%20counted!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_9%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EGive%20me%20an%20understanding%20heart%20so%20that%20I%20can%20govern%20your%20people%20well%20and%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20right%20and%20wrong.%20For%20who%20by%20himself%20is%20able%20to%20govern%20this%20great%20people%20of%20yours%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_10%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Lord%20was%20pleased%20that%20Solomon%20had%20asked%20for%20wisdom.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_11%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20God%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BBecause%20you%20have%20asked%20for%20wisdom%20in%20governing%20my%20people%20with%20justice%20and%20have%20not%20asked%20for%20a%20long%20life%20or%20wealth%20or%20the%20death%20of%20your%20enemies%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_12%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20give%20you%20what%20you%20asked%20for!%20I%20will%20give%20you%20a%20wise%20and%20understanding%20heart%20such%20as%20no%20one%20else%20has%20had%20or%20ever%20will%20have!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20will%20also%20give%20you%20what%20you%20did%20not%20ask%20for%26%23x2014%3Briches%20and%20fame!%20No%20other%20king%20in%20all%20the%20world%20will%20be%20compared%20to%20you%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_14%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20if%20you%20follow%20me%20and%20obey%20my%20decrees%20and%20my%20commands%20as%20your%20father%2C%20David%2C%20did%2C%20I%20will%20give%20you%20a%20long%20life.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_15%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Solomon%20woke%20up%20and%20realized%20it%20had%20been%20a%20dream.%20He%20returned%20to%20Jerusalem%20and%20stood%20before%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20Lord%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%2C%20where%20he%20sacrificed%20burnt%20offerings%20and%20peace%20offerings.%20Then%20he%20invited%20all%20his%20officials%20to%20a%20great%20banquet.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_16%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESolomon%20Judges%20Wisely%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3ESome%20time%20later%20two%20prostitutes%20came%20to%20the%20king%20to%20have%20an%20argument%20settled.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_17%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BPlease%2C%20my%20lord%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20one%20of%20them%20began%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bthis%20woman%20and%20I%20live%20in%20the%20same%20house.%20I%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20baby%20while%20she%20was%20with%20me%20in%20the%20house.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_18%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThree%20days%20later%20this%20woman%20also%20had%20a%20baby.%20We%20were%20alone%3B%20there%20were%20only%20two%20of%20us%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_19%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20her%20baby%20died%20during%20the%20night%20when%20she%20rolled%20over%20on%20it.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_20%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20she%20got%20up%20in%20the%20night%20and%20took%20my%20son%20from%20beside%20me%20while%20I%20was%20asleep.%20She%20laid%20her%20dead%20child%20in%20my%20arms%20and%20took%20mine%20to%20sleep%20beside%20her.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_21%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20in%20the%20morning%20when%20I%20tried%20to%20nurse%20my%20son%2C%20he%20was%20dead!%20But%20when%20I%20looked%20more%20closely%20in%20the%20morning%20light%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20it%20wasn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20my%20son%20at%20all.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_22%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20other%20woman%20interrupted%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%20certainly%20was%20your%20son%2C%20and%20the%20living%20child%20is%20mine.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BNo%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20first%20woman%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bthe%20living%20child%20is%20mine%2C%20and%20the%20dead%20one%20is%20yours.%26%23x201D%3B%20And%20so%20they%20argued%20back%20and%20forth%20before%20the%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_23%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20king%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLet%26%23x2019%3Bs%20get%20the%20facts%20straight.%20Both%20of%20you%20claim%20the%20living%20child%20is%20yours%2C%20and%20each%20says%20that%20the%20dead%20one%20belongs%20to%20the%20other.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_24%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20right%2C%20bring%20me%20a%20sword.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20a%20sword%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20king.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_25%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BCut%20the%20living%20child%20in%20two%2C%20and%20give%20half%20to%20one%20woman%20and%20half%20to%20the%20other!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_3_26%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20woman%20who%20was%20the%20real%20mother%20of%20the%20living%20child%2C%20and%20who%20loved%20him%20very%20much%2C%20cried%20out%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BOh%20no%2C%20my%20lord!%20Give%20her%20the%20child%26%23x2014%3Bplease%20do%20not%20kill%20him!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EBut%20the%20other%20woman%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BAll%20right%2C%20he%20will%20be%20neither%20yours%20nor%20mine%3B%20divide%20him%20between%20us!