2Fspan%3EThen%20we%20apostles%20can%20spend%20our%20time%20in%20prayer%20and%20teaching%20the%20word.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_6_5%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EEveryone%20liked%20this%20idea%2C%20and%20they%20chose%20the%20following%3A%20Stephen%20(a%20man%20full%20of%20faith%20and%20the%20Holy%20Spirit)%2C%20Philip%2C%20Procorus%2C%20Nicanor%2C%20Timon%2C%20Parmenas%2C%20and%20Nicolas%20of%20Antioch%20(an%20earlier%20convert%20to%20the%20Jewish%20faith).%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_6_6%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20seven%20were%20presented%20to%20the%20apostles%2C%20who%20prayed%20for%20them%20as%20they%20laid%20their%20hands%20on%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_6_7%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20message%20continued%20to%20spread.%20The%20number%20of%20believers%20greatly%20increased%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20and%20many%20of%20the%20Jewish%20priests%20were%20converted%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_6_8%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EStephen%20Is%20Arrested%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EStephen%2C%20a%20man%20full%20of%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20grace%20and%20power%2C%20performed%20amazing%20miracles%20and%20signs%20among%20the%20people.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_6_9%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20one%20day%20some%20men%20from%20the%20Synagogue%20of%20Freed%20Slaves%2C%20as%20